tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE StudentProgress (
    student_id INT,
    resource_id INT,
    progress INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES Students(student_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (resource_id) REFERENCES LearningResources(resource_id)
);

CREATE TABLE StudentProgress (
    student_id INT,
    resource_id INT,
    completion_status BOOLEAN,
    progress INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES Students(student_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (resource_id) REFERENCES LearningResources(resource_id)
);

CREATE TABLE AccessLogs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    resource_id INT,
    access_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES Students(student_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (resource_id) REFERENCES LearningResources(resource_id)
);

CREATE TABLE StudentProgress (
	student_id INT,
	resource_id INT,
	score INT,
	FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES Students(student_id),
	FOREIGN KEY (resource_id) REFERENCES LearningResources(resource_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ResourceAccess (
	student_id INT,
	resource_id INT,
	has_access BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
	FOREIGN KEY(student_id) REFERENCES Students(student_id),
	FOREIGN KEY(resource_id) REFERENCES LearningResources(resource_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ProgressHistory (
	student_id INT,
	progress_date DATE,
	progress_percentage INT,
	PRIMARY KEY (student_id, progress_date),
	FOREIGN KEY (student_id) REFERENCES Students(student_id)
);
